<h3>WnCC Machine Learning Learner Space 2026</h3>
<hr>
<p>In this notebook you will build a <strong>complete sentiment analysis pipeline</strong> - from raw text to a trained neural network - entirely from scratch.</p>
<p><strong>Your pipeline:</strong></p>
<pre><code><span><span class="mtk1">Raw&nbsp;Text&nbsp;→&nbsp;Clean&nbsp;→&nbsp;Tokenise&nbsp;→&nbsp;BoW&nbsp;/&nbsp;TF-IDF&nbsp;→&nbsp;</span><span class="mtk1">Logistic&nbsp;Regression&nbsp;(baseline)</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;MLP&nbsp;</span><span class="mtk1">(neural&nbsp;network)</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;</span><span class="mtk1">Evaluate&nbsp;with&nbsp;F1,&nbsp;Confusion&nbsp;Matrix</span></span>
</code></pre><p><strong>Rules:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>You may use <code>numpy</code>, <code>matplotlib</code>, <code>sklearn</code> for utilities</li>
<li>For the MLP section, use <strong>PyTorch</strong> (or NumPy if you prefer)</li>
<li>Do NOT just call <code>sklearn.Pipeline</code> and call it done. Implement the concepts.</li>
<li>Every <code># YOUR CODE HERE</code> block must be filled in</li>
</ul>
